{"tid":1478541,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唉，又要幫勇武派執屎…","createTime":"2019-08-16T14:25:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-16T15:01:27.000Z","uid":53855,"like":30,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c0d0af28bcb6956bde7dd860b7e7e1fd4ad0e98d","tid":1478541,"uid":53855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T14:25:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我之前講過呢句，我衷心咁同各位前線講聲對唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n我之前機場嗰晚，自己戇鳩，係咁屌勇武暴力，我反省咗幾日，如果冇勇武，根本就無今日，勇武前線咁撚辛苦又可能比人拉，我咁樣講根本係一樣背叛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />前線睇到甚至可能會心灰唔再去，咁場運動可能就會散&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n從今以後，我唔會再割蓆！亦同時希望之前睇到我留言嘅前線可以原諒我。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不割蓆不譴責不篤灰</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">c朗＞美斯</span></span>"},{"pid":"beb37b354aa67399d537231db7da713960843472","tid":1478541,"uid":53855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T14:27:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"11766c5cad0ed398c52c08b5401a50165240e158","tid":1478541,"uid":303304,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T14:29:02.000Z","msg":"好多人話818有鬼，點算？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1478490\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1478490</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f73ea0e1618399342a973245264e49d78c8c7af7","tid":1